==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Questionless
<hw>Ques"tion*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Unquestioning;
incurious.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

