==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: questionless
<hw>ques"tion*less</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Beyond a question or
doubt; doubtless; certainly.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>What it was in the apostles' time, that, <qex>questionless</qex>,
it must be still.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>questionnaire</ent>⟦br⟧
